879
01:43:21,840 --> 01:43:24,400
Pogledaj, čvrtič, svakako je predivan.

880
01:43:24,560 --> 01:43:24,960
Da se ovu.

881
01:43:26,480 --> 01:43:27,280
Budem pogledat.

882
01:43:30,080 --> 01:43:32,080
